---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "B2B Sales & Outbound Articles | CallTeam"
description: "Practical B2B articles on lead generation, outbound calling, appointment setting, sales pipeline, and revenue execution from CallTeam."
permalink: "/articles/"
---

<section class="hero">
  <div>
    <h1>B2B sales and outbound <span class="highlight">articles</span>.</h1>
    <p>Practical guides on lead generation, outbound calling, appointment setting, pipeline, and sales execution for B2B teams.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container-wide">
    <div class="section-label">Articles</div>
    <h2>Latest posts.</h2>
    <div class="service-grid">
      {% for article in collections.articles | reverse %}
      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>{{ article.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ article.data.description }}</p>
        <a href="{{ article.url }}" class="card-link">Read more →</a>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
